{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">了解液体温度计的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原理，会用常见温度计测量温度。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">温度计是测量温度的工具，温度计是利用物体的热胀冷缩性质工作的。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">温度计、冷水烧杯、温水烧杯、热水烧杯</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.观察温度计，确认</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">温度计</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的量程和</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分度值</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.用温度计分别测量</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">三杯水的温度。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.记录数据。</span></span></span></p>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border:none; font-family:Calibri; font-size:13px; margin-left:9px; margin-right:9px; width:500px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:98px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:85px\">\n\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">冷水</span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:94px\">\n\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">温水</span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:99px\">\n\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">热水</span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:98px\">\n\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">温度</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">℃</span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:85px\">\n\t\t\t<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:94px\">\n\t\t\t<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:99px\">\n\t\t\t<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">1.温度计可以测量温度；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">冷水、温水、热水的温度不同。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">温度计使用方法：</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">1.手拿温度计的上端<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2.将温度计下端浸入水中，不能碰到容器的底与壁；</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">3.视线与温度计液面持平；</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">4.在液柱不再上升或下降时读数；</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">5.读数时温度计不能离开被测的水。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}